builder-description =
    FreeSynergy Builder is the creation and publishing tool for FreeSynergy packages.

    Import a Docker Compose file to automatically generate a container package with
    Quadlet service files, variables, and field help. Build bridge definitions that
    let services expose data through the message bus. Or create any package type
    from scratch with the guided wizard.

    Packages created with Builder can be validated locally and published to the
    official Store catalog or any community repository.

builder-features =
    - Docker Compose import → container package generator
    - Automatic variable detection with type inference
    - Bridge definition builder for service integrations
    - Guided wizard for all package types (app, container, theme, widget, task)
    - Local validation: completeness check, CI rules, icon check
    - Publish to Store catalog via git or pull request
    - AI-assisted description and help text generation (requires fs-ai)
